---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | MoveCostMatrix" description="MoveCostMatrix privacy policy. We do not collect, store, or share any personal data. Everything runs in your browser." canonical="/privacy">
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      "itemListElement": [
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://movecostmatrix.com/" },
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Privacy Policy", "item": "https://movecostmatrix.com/privacy" }
      ]
    }
  </script>
  <Nav currentPath="/privacy" />

  <main>
  <section class="bg-canvas px-4 pb-28 pt-16 sm:pb-36 sm:pt-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-mute">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-mute">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-body content">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Our Privacy Promise</h2>
        <p>MoveCostMatrix is a privacy-focused moving cost calculator. We designed the service so that your calculator entries, locations, and cost estimates are processed entirely in your browser. You do not need to create an account or provide an email address to use our service. We use Google Analytics to monitor anonymous traffic trends to help us maintain and improve the site.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">What Data We Collect</h2>
        <p>We do not collect, store, or process any personal information or calculation details. All calculation data — including origin and destination entries, distance results, and cost estimates — runs entirely in your browser using JavaScript. We do collect aggregated, anonymized website usage statistics via Google Analytics (see the <a href="#analytics" class="text-link underline">Analytics section</a> below).</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>When you enter a postal code, the calculator calls the <a href="https://zippopotam.us" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-link underline">zippopotam.us API</a> to look up coordinates for distance calculation. This is a free public service. We also load Google Analytics scripts to monitor site usage.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Cookies</h2>
        <p>Google Analytics sets cookies on your device to collect anonymized usage statistics. We do not use advertising cookies, marketing trackers, or tracking pixels. The only data we store locally is your dark-mode preference (<code class="rounded bg-canvas-soft px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs">movecost-theme</code>). It stays in your browser and is never sent to us or anyone else.</p>

        <h2 id="analytics" class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Analytics</h2>
        <p>We use Google Analytics (tag ID <code class="rounded bg-canvas-soft px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs">G-CNSF2RTM9W</code>) to collect anonymous traffic data. This helps us understand how visitors use the calculator, which pages they visit, and how we can improve. The data includes your device type, browser, and pages viewed — but it does not identify you. To opt out, install the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-link underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a> or block cookies in your browser.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Since we collect no data, there is nothing to retain. Your calculation results exist only in your browser tab and disappear when you close or refresh the page.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>If we make material changes to this policy, we will update the &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date at the top. Because we collect no data, any changes will relate to new third-party integrations or service architecture, which we will clearly document.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, <a href="/contact" class="text-link underline">contact us here</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  </main>

  <Footer currentPath="/privacy" />
</Layout>
